n AI chips, reporting a remarkable 69% year-over-year increase in Q1 fiscal 2026 revenue, largely attributed to a 73% growth in its Data Center segment. The document underscores these companies\' strategic innovations and growth drivers, encouraging investors to focus on these aspects rather than merely following trends.\", \"topics\": [\"financial_planning\", \"financial_health\", \"budgeting\", \"cashflow_management\"], \"tools_relevant\": [\"inflows_tool\", \"outflow_tool\"], \"trust_level\": \"internal\", \"document_type\": \"kb_article\", \"persona_tags\": [\"Budget-Oriented\", \"Cash Flow Conscious\", \"Income-Oriented Planner\"]}, \"excluded_embed_metadata_keys\": [\"file_size\", \"creation_date\", \"last_modified_date\", \"last_accessed_date\"], \"excluded_llm_metadata_keys\": [\"file_size\", \"creation_date\", \"last_modified_date\", \"last_accessed_date\"], \"relationships\": {\"1\": {\"node_id\": \"/home/siddhardhan/workspace/work/1_datalign/1_1_datalign_src/halo-rag-1-1/halo_rag/articles/Aligned Perspective - The Best AI Stocks of 2025.txt\", \"node_type\": \"4\", \"metadata\": {\"file_path\": \"/home/siddhardhan/workspace/work/1_datalign/1_1_datalign_src/halo-rag-1-1/halo_rag/articles/Aligned Perspective - The Best AI Stocks of 2025.txt\", \"file_name\": \"Aligned Perspective - The Best AI Stocks of 2025.txt\", \"file_type\": \"text/plain\", \"file_size\": 11242, \"creation_date\": \"2025-08-12\", \"last_modified_date\": \"2025-08-12\", \"doc_hash\": \"c52a8c49d9e817523f77be3bd33f3d35e2476e5da45f22a5df9f2eb146551c63\", \"source\": \"https://www.datalignadvisory.com/finding-your-fit-top-ai-stocks-of-2025/\"}, \"hash\": \"3b4ad1904163f3961963b0c4bed546f395da50addc8f24a6fa1b2b64ad811b6a\", \"class_name\": \"RelatedNodeInfo\"}, \"2\": {\"node_id\": \"e35a5f24-9a4c-41c8-87ab-f806de445203\", \"node_type\": \"1\", \"metadata\": {\"file_path\": \"/home/siddhardhan/workspace/work/1_datalign/1_1_datalign_src/halo-rag-1-1/halo_rag/articles/Aligned Perspective - Th